      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it's been babied since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel! If you\u2019re looking for something in truly pristine, showroom condition that drives like an absolute dream, you\u2019ve found it. It\u2019s spotless inside and out. Drop me a message if you want to come see it\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S54 inline-six heritage. This vehicle features a comprehensive mechanical pedigree, including a documented dual-VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement to ensure optimal valve timing and bottom-end longevity. The chassis is structurally sound with professional subframe reinforcement already completed. Drive is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains factory kinematics with fresh bushings and dampers, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of a pristine M-division product. Finished in original paint with an immaculate interior, this car represents a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
