    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the pre-owned experience. This vehicle is in showroom-perfect condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, completely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium hand-stitched leather remains supple and matte, with no creasing or bolster wear, and still retains its original factory scent. Every technological feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of preventative maintenance records performed exclusively by certified technicians. From the unblemished 19-inch alloy wheels to the crystal-clear LED headlight housings, every inch of this car has been curated for the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the showroom floor.",
